=======================================================================
		OpenAtom Massively Parallel Code v1.5a
=======================================================================

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 DIRECTORY STRUCTURE
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The important directories in this distribution are:

Charm++ driver      :   src_charm_driver
PINY physics        :   src_piny_physics_v1.0
Math routines       :   src_mathlib

Test configurations :   tests
Build files         :   makefiles

Documentation       :   doc
Simulation data     :   data

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 INSTALLATION 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
To build OpenAtom read the INSTALL file

